
<p><a href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-02-11/apple-s-ios-26-4-siri-update-runs-into-snags-in-internal-testing-ios-26-5-27">Bloomberg reports</a>&nbsp;that the new Gemini-powered Siri features planned for iOS 26.4 are being pushed back. Some to iOS 26.5 in May. Some to iOS 27 in September.</p>



<p>Have you ever felt like Charlie Brown running to kick the football, only to notice, at the last minute, that Lucy is holding it?</p>



